snippet.title: Dwarven Realms Season 0 Coming Soon
snippet.description:
Hey warriors, adventurers, oath keepers and protectors of the realm! 
Dwarven Realms season 0 will begin Saturday, October 22nd. If you are interested in helping to test and play the new season join our Discord. Everyone already with a Steam key should be able to participate. There will be prizes for the winners. More details will be revealed soon.

Join our discord here: https://discord.gg/sKD5hbBEQg
